    <p>Rozenkelim sources vintage and antique rugs globally, showcasing and selling them through their online platform and Haarlem-based showroom. Rozenkelim operates a lightning-fast Rapidez webshop with custom design. The Rozenkelim Rapidez webshop is developed in such a way that it requires minimal Magento 2 extensions. Many of the functionalities that were previously added through Magento 2 extensions are now managed through Statamic. Rozenkelim's Rapidez webshop utilizes the JustBetter checkout package with Multisafepay.</p>
